- User can approve/reject sources.
- User can review source-linked documents.
- User can extract deterministic mock signals.
- User can cluster signals into candidate trends.
- User can approve/reject/edit trends.
- Approved trends appear in Insights.
- Rejected trends do not appear in Insights.
- Every trend has traceable evidence.
- Every evidence item links back to source and document.
- Tests are written before implementation.
- All tests pass.
- No external LLM/API dependency is required.

