====================================================
IMPORTANT IMPLEMENTATION NOTES
====================================================

Do not generate trends without evidence.
Do not hide uncertainty.
Do not combine likelihood and confidence.
Do not treat all sources equally.
Do not allow rejected sources to influence default insights.
Do not auto-approve AI-generated trends.
Do not create random or non-deterministic scores.
Do not introduce real API calls in Phase 1.
Do not skip E2E tests.
Do not proceed to the next implementation step until the current tests pass.